    {
      "id": "99eb8417_4b73b843",
      "file_path": "datafile-app-server/src/main/docker/Dockerfile",
      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 42,
      "message": "When I try build image using this MR i get error: \n\"can't find uid for user $user: no such user: $user\"\nUsing COPY resolved this issue on my local machine. \nI am Using Docker v19.0.3\n\nDocker (until version 20.10.0 - released 2020-12-08) has issue with ADD --chown - it not allow to use user/group as ENV or ARG - it was resolved here https://github.com/moby/buildkit/pull/1473 (v 20.10.0 )\n\nI am afraid that Jenkins CI don't use latest version of docker - so we could have problem with building images on Jenkins.",
      "author": {
